{
  "stem": "4284.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ghettos were usually districts of a city, major city-- Warsaw, Lodz-- that would be fenced in, electrified, into which all the Jews that they had in Poland, in Lodz, in Warsaw or ultimately from Germany, confined in an area where you had-- I believe we had in one place in Lodz 27,000 rooms with 160,000 people.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So 1939 and thereafter, things have changed in Germany because of the wartime existence and now the Jews were considered to be not only enemies, but traitors.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because everything now changed rapidly to the possibility of sending Jews out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1941, January 1941, we were told by the Jewish center that deportations will take place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we received a message from the German official, basically police, that you have to report, let's say, on Monday at 8 o'clock in a huge facility.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like most cities we know would be a convention center which was empty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was supposed to be filled with Jews destined to go somewhere, destination unknown.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans do not rely on volunteer reporting and have always used darkness, the nighttime, including the German shepherds, including sticks, guns, rifles, butts and so on to invade your home and in the darkness of night simply grab you.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You did have your little suitcase packed because you're not allowed to take much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just the very minimal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Certainly no luggage possibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here we were, supposedly reporting on Monday, when on Saturday night they came and grabbed my parents and myself out of the apartment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were shut on a truck where other people had already been collected, and then we were delivered to this convention center.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We sat there, and we sat there for two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
